title: Jay Larson
description: Jay Larson (Comedy Central, Late Late Show, CD "Self Diagnosed") is one of Pete's absolute favorite people in the world and hands-down a spectacular guest to make things weird. They talk gnomes, comedy, gnomes, marriage, and a little bit more about gnomes. Holy shit! Hilarious. Weird. A delight. It's a good one folks. Please enjoy you weirdos!!
